eiträge konturieren die Relevanz der Grammatikforschung für die Anforderungen eines zeitgemäßen Deutschunterrichts im Spannungsfeld zwischen Grammatik-, Literatur-, Sprach- und Textkompetenz und konfrontieren etablierte Auffassungen zur Grammatikarbeit in Schule und Unterricht mit gegenwärtigen Problemen.  aThis volume draws together current studies and research findings from the fields of university research into German grammar and grammar teaching in schools. The contributors outline the relevance of grammatical research in meeting the demands of present-day school German teaching between the requirements of competence in grammar, literature, language and text, and confront established views of grammar teachingin schools with topical problems.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aGerman languagexGrammar. 4aDeutschunterricht. 4aGrammatik. 4aKongress. 4aMünster ‹Westfalen, 2005›. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aDürscheid, Christa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEichler, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFunke, Reinold, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrießhaber, Wilhelm, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHinze, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlotz, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKöpcke, Klaus-Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKöpcke, Klaus-Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOssner, Jakob, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRedder, Angelika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb